CompanyDescription.label: Company Description
CompanyDescription.value: Vivid Seats Inc is an online ticket marketplace for connecting fans to live events, artists. It is the official ticketing partner by brands in the entertainment industry providing tickets for sports, concerts, theatres, and comedy. It operates in two segments namely marketplace and resale.
